replies.body:
How to Focus in Bronze:

* Kill the thing that is attacking you and can kill you {{champion:7}} {{champion:104}} 
* Kill the thing that is attacking and can't kill you but imminent follow up can. {{champion:53}} {{champion:266}} 
* Kill the thing that you're in range of that is doing the damage to your team. {{champion:110}}  {{champion:103}} 
* Kill who you're in range of that your team ignores but still does damage. {{champion:80}} {{champion:64}} 
* Kill the thing that is obstructing you from killing anything else {{champion:57}}{{champion:201}}

But aren't we always told to not focus tanks? 

You say to focus the tanks, they make you kill able.. How? Because they TANK all the damage while the people who deal damage are taking out everyone who's more squishy. 

Idiots focus tanks.. That's like.. Focusing the Leona support before getting the twitch down in botlane.. How does that turn out? 

